 "material_discrepancy_FY2021_22": {
  "finding": "DPIIT's cumulative and annual tables CONTRADICT each other for FY2021-22. Between the March-2021 and March-2022 vintages, 'State Not Indicated' FELL by 322.21 USD mn and the same money reappears across five named states. DPIIT re-attributed previously unallocated inflow inside the cumulative table but never back-fitted the annual columns that Parliament's answer reproduces.",
  "implication": "For FY2021-22 the DERIVED figure is the fresher one and the published annual column is stale. Maharashtra's FY2021-22 inflow is understated by 293.32 USD mn (1.90%) in the published annual series.",
