 "immaterial_negatives": "Four sub-0.01 sign flips (Arunachal, Ladakh, Nagaland) are artefacts of DPIIT dropping from 4 decimal places to 2 between vintages, not restatements.",
 "cannot_be_derived": "FY2020-21. State-wise data begins October 2019, so the March-2021 table is an 18-month stock, and no March-2020 vintage was retrievable (the Dec-2019 factsheet covers only Oct-Dec 2019). Use the directly-published FY2020-21 column instead.",
